Aura of the Sun.MOD							SOURCEPAGE:p.30		DESC:Fills an area with light that damages undead and hampers magical darkness.
Backblast.MOD								SOURCEPAGE:p.30		DESC:Grants fire resistance 10 and functions like Spell Turning with respect to spells with the Fire descriptor that are targeted on you.
Bloodbriars.MOD								SOURCEPAGE:p.30		DESC:Wraps target in invisible briars that deal 1d8 points of damage per round if movement is attempted.
Clearstone.MOD								SOURCEPAGE:p.31		DESC:Makes rock and stone transparent.
Crushing Sphere.MOD							SOURCEPAGE:p.31		DESC:Force globe traps and crushes subject for 3d6 points of nonlethal damage per round.
Ebon Ray of Doom.MOD						SOURCEPAGE:p.31		DESC:Black energy prevents magical healing and special healing abilities from functioning.
Ghost Pipes.MOD								SOURCEPAGE:p.31		DESC:Causes an instrument to float above the ground and play itself.
Know Bloodline.MOD							SOURCEPAGE:p.32		DESC:Reveals target's type, race, subrace, and all subtypes possessed.
Mailed Might of the Magelords.MOD			SOURCEPAGE:p.32		DESC:Field of force around subject grants +8 armor bonus, immunity to 2nd-level and lower Force spells, and DR 5/magic.
Nar Fiendbond.MOD							SOURCEPAGE:p.32		DESC:Grants the subject the half-fiend template. This costs the caster 500xp per character level of the half-fiend created.
Nezram's Amethyst Aura.MOD					SOURCEPAGE:p.32		DESC:Prevents poisons and diseases from affecting the subject.
Nezram's Emerald Energy Shield.MOD			SOURCEPAGE:p.32		DESC:Grants immunity to deafness effects and language-dependent, mind-affecting effects, plus sonic resistance 10 and a +4 bonus on saves against spells and effects with the Sonic descriptor to which the subject isn't already immune.
Nezram's Sapphire Screen of Shielding.MOD	SOURCEPAGE:p.33		DESC:Moving shield of force grants +4 bonus to AC against ranged attacks and DR 10/magic against all other attacks.
Ray of Resurgence.MOD						SOURCEPAGE:p.33		DESC:Yellow light restores %1 of Strength damage, negates penalties to Strength (up to 1d6+%2) and either converts exhaustion to fatigue or removes fatigue|min(CASTERLEVEL, 5)|min(CASTERLEVEL, 5)
Sakkratar's Triple Strike.MOD				SOURCEPAGE:p.33		DESC:Grants each subject two extra attacks with a held melee weapon at its highest base attack bonus; grants the Keen and Flaming Burst abilities to melee weapons held by subjects.
Sandblast.MOD								SOURCEPAGE:p.33		DESC:Cone of sand and wind deals 6d8 points of damage and blows away opponents.
Shalantha's Delicate Disk.MOD				SOURCEPAGE:p.33		DESC:Conjures disk that can store a single spell of up to 5th level and release it when broken.
Srinshee's Spell Shift.MOD					SOURCEPAGE:p.34		DESC:Instead of countering another's spell, you can apply a metamagic feat to it, manipulate one of its properties, or stun the caster.
Storm Shield.MOD							SOURCEPAGE:p.34		DESC:Glowing sphere absorbs %1 points of electricity damage from effects that pass within 30 ft.|(CASTERLEVEL * 20)
Sun Scepter.MOD								SOURCEPAGE:p.34		DESC:Scepter of light functions as a melee weapon with the Axiomatic, Disruption, and Flaming Burst special abilities.
Theskyn's Hearty Heave.MOD					SOURCEPAGE:p.35		DESC:Blast of force pushes away creatures surrounding you as though via a bull rush maneuver by a foe of Large size with a Strength score equal to %1|min(CASTERLEVEL, 5)
Toothed Tentacle.MOD						SOURCEPAGE:p.35		DESC:Shadowy tentacle ending in three mouths (each AC 15, HP %1) projects from your hand. The mouths can strike foes within 10 feet of each other independently, dealing 2d6 points of damage each.
Tyche's Touch.MOD							SOURCEPAGE:p.35		DESC:Confers a decreasing sacred bonus or penalty (beginning at +4 or -4) on the subjects next four saving throws.


